<li id="cite_note-laceleb-138"><b><a href="#cite_ref-laceleb_138-0" title="">^</a></b> Joel Sappell and Robert W. Welkos, Times Staff Writers, <a href="http://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-scientology062790a,0,3614832.story" class="external text" title="http://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-scientology062790a,0,3614832.story" rel="nofollow">Courting the Power Brokers</a> The Los Angeles Times, June 27, 1990</li>
</ol>
